folder: Bay Ridge Avenue & Narrows Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Bay Ridge Avenue - Narrows Avenue
text:
Bay Ridge Ave., west of Narrows Ave.  At the left foreground, is Narrows Ave.  In the far background, is the Bay Ridge Staten Island Ferry.
May 10, 1929.

P.L. Sperr.

folder: Bay Ridge Avenue & Narrows Avenue, Brooklyn, NY

text:
Bay Ridge Ave., south side, east from, but not including Narrows Ave.
April 29, 1929.

P.L. Sperr.
